title: Times New Roman
content:
Hi there,

I need help identifying this typeface. I don’t think it’s Times New Roman or Dutch 801

[http://www.timwan.co.uk/files/gimgs/31\_dsc0522.jpg](http://web.archive.org/web/20140713101937/http:/www.timwan.co.uk/files/gimgs/31_dsc0522.jpg "http://www.timwan.co.uk/files/gimgs/31\_dsc0522.jpg")

More images: [http://www.timwan.co.uk/index.php?/work-2/garry-barker/](http://web.archive.org/web/20140713101937/http:/www.timwan.co.uk/index.php?/work-2/garry-barker/ "http://www.timwan.co.uk/index.php?/work-2/garry-barker/")

Thank You!
author: G.O.G.

comments.content: Starling is very good option but having a closer look makes me thinking it could be [Times](http://web.archive.org/web/20140713101937/http:/www.myfonts.com/search/times) and probably one of its more contrasted version [Times Ten](http://web.archive.org/web/20140713101937/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/adobe/times-ten/).
